www.TeamHigherGround.com is dedicated to making a positive impact on, and through, our valued clients.

As an extension of our mission, starting in 2011, we will dedicate a portion of each client's professional fees to empowering entrepreneurs around the world!

Our sincere gratitude to our clients for supporting us in our intention to make the world better through inspired entrepreneurs the world over!
lenders.occupational_info:
Higher Ground is an International Business Improvement Organization supporting its global clients from its bases in Vancouver, Calgary, Toronto and Montreal, Canada, and Seattle, USA. We support clients in North America, South America, Europe, Asia, Australia, and Africa.
 
Higher Ground has an outstanding track record of working with leaders and teams in many of the world’s most successful organizations. Breakthrough performance and outstanding results are what our clients want our help with. We achieve results through inspirational Team Building programs, targeted Experiential Training Programs (Learning Adventures), and Business Transformation processes.
 
Higher Ground works to develop leaders and teams and to remove the barriers which cause the ‘normal’ dysfunction so prevalent in corporate life today. Our programs and processes integrate with yours ensuring an inescapable collective focus on overcoming business challenges and achieving the desired results. 
 
Higher Ground was founded in 1995 to enable more people to enjoy going to work inspired and effectively getting their job done. The result of our work is leaders and team members going to work each day more fulfilled and organizations more capable of thriving in today's increasingly complex and ever-changing climate.
